data.name: label4.Text
data.value: NOTE: Make sure the server you join is in the region of the world you live in! (i.e West US, East US, Europe, etc). If you have a problem where you can't see your character, REGENERATE YOUR PLAYER ID THEN REJOIN THE SERVER. If you tried to connect to the server and you get an error, REJOIN THE SERVER. If the server requires a different port than the normal ROBLOX port (53640), change it in the OPTIONS tab.

data.name: label30.Text
data.value: WARNING: This client loads assets directly from a server. This means that you may not be able to play it over a LAN or local connection without internet access. This may also mean that some things won't load (i.e the healthbar)
